<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Your Shopi Order Confirmation</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333;">
  <h2 style="color: #0e0e0f;">Thank You for Your Order, <%= username %>!</h2>

  <p>We are excited to let you know that your order has been received and is now being processed.</p>

  <h3>Order Details:</h3>
  <p><strong>Order ID:</strong>
    <%= orderPublicId %>
  </p>
  <p><strong>Total Amount:</strong> $<%= totalAmount %>
  </p>

  <h3>Shipping Information:</h3>
  <p><strong>Address:</strong>
    <%= shippingAddress %>
  </p>
  <p><strong>City:</strong>
    <%= shippingCity %>
  </p>
  <p><strong>Country:</strong>
    <%= shippingCountry %>
  </p>

  <p>You can view your order details by clicking the link below:</p>
  <p>
    <a href="<%= orderLink %>" style="color: #4aa1f3; text-decoration: none;">
      View Your Order
    </a>
  </p>

  <p>If the link above doesnâ€™t work, copy and paste the URL into a new browser window:</p>
  <p>
    <%= orderLink %>
  </p>

